text: Edita Vilkevičiūtė (born 1 January 1989) is a Lithuanian model. Throughout her whole career, she has appeared in 25 Vogue covers. In 2015, she was one of the highest paid models in the world thanks to the frangrace ads for Roberto Cavalli and Viktor & Rolf. Category:1989 births Category:Living people Category:Lithuanian people
title: Edita Vilkevičiūtė
